OL,3,C#36 million needed for Condor Ferries
OL,4,Cto operate in Jersey
OL,6,FHe explained Condor would likely
OL,7,Frequire #36 million in funding in
OL,8,Forder to outsee its contractual
OL,9,Fobligations, adding that both Jersey
OL,10,Fand Guernsey have already paid
OL,11,Fapproximately #3 million as part of a
OL,12,Fcontingency to keep the company afloat.
OL,14,FIt follows a slew of announcements
OL,15,Fyesterday that included:
OL,17,FDeputy Kirsten Morel has also outlined
OL,18,Fa new ferry process for the final two
OL,19,Fbidders, which he described as "short
OL,20,Fand simple":
