OL,3,C#36 million needed for Condor Ferries
OL,4,Cto operate in Jersey
OL,6,FDeputy Morel used his parliamentary
OL,7,Fprivilege to summarise his concerns
OL,8,Fwith Condor Ferries, admitting that if
OL,9,FCondor did not receive the next
OL,10,Fcontract to operate the Channel
OL,11,FIslands, they could fold before March
OL,12,F2025.
OL,14,FHe told the States Assembly: "Last
OL,15,Fyear, I received two requests for
OL,16,Ffinancial support from Condor Ferries.
OL,17,FThe first was for an 80 million euro
OL,18,Fguarantee and the second for 40
OL,19,Fmillion euros, with 10 million needed
OL,20,Furgently.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
