OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1731518246
OL,3,C#36 million needed for Condor Ferries
OL,4,Cto operate in Jersey
OL,6,F"Condor's insolvency was ultimately
OL,7,Fprevented without the need for public
OL,8,Ffunds from Jersey but we decided, with
OL,9,FGuernsey, to protect our lifeline
OL,10,Fservices by engaging contingency at a
OL,11,Fcost so far, of approximately #3
OL,12,Fmillion to each island."
OL,14,FHe goes on to explain: "I have
OL,15,Frepeatedly sought reassurance from
OL,16,FCondor Ferries and their shareholders
OL,17,Fthat the company will improve its
OL,18,Ffinancial position and be able to
OL,19,Fcomplete its contractual obligations
OL,20,Funder the current operating agreement.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
