OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1731518246
OL,3,C#36 million needed for Condor Ferries
OL,4,Cto operate in Jersey
OL,6,F"I am yet to receive these
OL,7,Freassurances.
OL,9,F"Condor Ferries would likely require
OL,10,Ffunding from the Government of Jersey
OL,11,Fof up to #36 million in order to see
OL,12,Fout its contractual obligations."
OL,14,FDeputy Morel also confirmed that while
OL,15,Fthe bid was made in Brittany Ferries'
OL,16,Fname, they have received confirmation
OL,17,Fthat the Operating Agreement would be
OL,18,Fsigned with Condor Ferries and not
OL,19,Fwith Brittany.
