OL,6,FHe explains: "Our analysis of Condor's
OL,7,Fbusiness plan included growth plans
OL,8,Fthat were deemed to be unlikely to
OL,9,Fdeliver as they were overly optimistic
OL,10,Fgiven the high levels of debt in the
OL,11,Fcompany,
OL,13,F"Whilst there has been a promise of
OL,14,Frestructure, (debt) continues to
OL,15,Fremain (very high) and most
OL,16,Fimportantly, their promises of future
OL,17,Ffleet investment are wholly dependent
OL,18,Fon successful refinancing in 3 and a
OL,19,Fhalf years' time.
