OL,6,F"Therefore, there is no guarantee of
OL,7,Fthere ever being future fleet
OL,8,Finvestment."
OL,10,FLater in his statement, Deputy Morel
OL,11,Fsignalled that DFDS Seaway's original
OL,12,Fbid was a better choice for the island.
OL,14,FDeputy Morel says: "By any common
OL,15,Fsense reading of the two bids, (DFDS)
OL,16,Fis clearly the better of the two,
OL,17,Fpromising more fleet investment, more
OL,18,Fquickly and with a more stable
OL,19,Fcorporation, which is over 40% owned
OL,20,Fby a long-established charitable
OL,21,Ffoundation for mariners.
OL,26,@wD@`pmwD@epn
