OL,3,C#36 million needed for Condor Ferries
OL,4,Cto operate in Jersey
OL,6,F"However, DFDS' bid failed on a
OL,7,Ftechnical legal point, one which I
OL,8,Fcould not personally fathom because
OL,9,Fthe legal element was still to be
OL,10,Fnegotiated but which I accepted.
OL,12,F"However, their elimination did not
OL,13,Fmean that I could easily jump to award
OL,14,Fto Condor Ferries for all of the
OL,15,Freasons I have just stated."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
