OL,3,C#36 million needed for Condor Ferries
OL,4,Cto operate in Jersey
OL,6,FDeputy Morel also revealed that DFDS
OL,7,Fhas named a fleet for their primary
OL,8,Fmobilised fleet based on part of what
OL,9,Fthey own and what they can charter,
OL,10,Fand provided levels of charter for
OL,11,Ftheir start-up fleet that would not
OL,12,Finclude Condor.
OL,14,FDeputy Raluca Kovacs asked the
OL,15,Fminister if he was confident whether
OL,16,Fthey would have a ferry service by
OL,17,FMarch 1st, to which the Minister said
OL,18,Fhe was confident.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
