OL,3,C#36 million needed for Condor Ferries
OL,4,Cto operate in Jersey
OL,6,FThe statement received support from
OL,7,Fsome States Members, with Deputy
OL,8,FJonathan Renouf saying it comes as a
OL,9,F"huge relief" for islanders to be put
OL,10,Fin "clear and simple terms".
OL,12,FDeputy Morel says: "We need to ensure
OL,13,Ffinancial sustainability of a 15-year
OL,14,Fcontract and we need to ensure
OL,15,Finvestment in vessels.
OL,17,F"We need to ensure our freight aims
OL,18,Fare met and that means delivering a
OL,19,Fflat rate card as required by the
OL,20,Ftender process - something which
OL,21,FCondor has failed to deliver so far.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
