OL,3,C#36 million needed for Condor Ferries
OL,4,Cto operate in Jersey
OL,6,F"We cannot be forced into a decision
OL,7,Fwhich we believe is wrong for Jersey
OL,8,Fand the joint process was on the cusp
OL,9,Fof delivering just that, a service
OL,10,Fthat delivered uncertainty and risk
OL,11,Ffor the islanders of Jersey.
OL,13,F"This new and fast process will allow
OL,14,Fus to make the right decision for
OL,15,FJersey's future lifeline ferry
OL,16,Fservices."
